{"tid":2449064,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前SKE48偶像山田樹奈因涉嫌欺詐被捕：誘導購買金融投資二元期權","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T11:51:33.000Z","uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa2c9117470b76b31bda5cdbd6610cb355c9fce","tid":2449064,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/yamada-juna-fraud/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fentertainment%2Fyamada-juna-fraud%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=7408ff77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/yamada-juna-fraud/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73MW1xt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73MW1xt.jpg&h=3a0fb255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，據日本產經新聞報導，愛知縣警方拘捕涉嫌欺詐及違法特定商取法的4名男女，當中包含SKE48前成員，現為無職的山田樹奈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sankei_news/status/1371743212981813251?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsankei_news%2Fstatus%2F1371743212981813251%3Fs%3D21&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=f9f1a0a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsankei_news%2Fstatus%2F1371743212981813251%3Fs%3D21&h=58c3d026\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sankei_news/status/1371743212981813251?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">涉嫌騙取網上結識男上班族50萬 受害人共約100人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n據報導所指，SKE48前成員山田樹奈涉嫌於去年1月，在交友網站上結識當時23歲的男性上班族，並以教投資儲蓄的技巧為名，騙取該名男性50萬日圓學費，據報指今次涉及的金融商品為「二元期權」。<br />\n<br />\n山田樹奈和其餘被拘捕的主犯車館宙生等3人都使用了假名，對於調查他們表示「並沒有想過要騙取金錢」否認指控。按警方推測，估計以主犯車館宙生為中心，他們已在交友網站及社交媒體上詐騙約100人，並詐取約5800萬日圓。警方現時以懷疑欺詐和違反《特定商業交易法》（虛假陳述）拘捕嫌犯，他們會再追查他們有否犯下其他罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yahoonewstopics/status/1371733307273084934?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyahoonewstopics%2Fstatus%2F1371733307273084934%3Fs%3D21&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=8bc88935\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyahoonewstopics%2Fstatus%2F1371733307273084934%3Fs%3D21&h=18e5ca2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yahoonewstopics/status/1371733307273084934?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">SKE48前成員山田樹奈資料簡介 4年前曾擔任一日警官</span></span><br />\n<br />\n山田樹奈於1998年5月25日（22歲）出生，出生地為愛知縣。她於2013年加入SKE48，在2015年昇格為Team S所屬的正式成員，並於2019年畢業。山田樹奈在2017年時更曾經在故鄉愛知縣擔任一日警官，現今卻涉嫌因犯罪被捕，令人感到可惜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rv6LUUp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRv6LUUp.jpg&h=6524d8d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b723e30df81cbff7b8bdd12f8534652829c1f6fa","tid":2449064,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"有冇ching當年揸過手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a85ee929e0e9b2546bc795a50c6b58d45c38b0a","tid":2449064,"uid":7903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:21:38.000Z","msg":"日本版微信雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf680c8ec60947a0e629bf33a8e55551ea144c18","tid":2449064,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a85ee929e0e9b2546bc795a50c6b58d45c38b0a","tid":2449064,"uid":7903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:21:38.000Z","msg":"日本版微信雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"大把line g"},{"pid":"30fa56707c4add986e390b1cf6935fae257fc1d0","tid":2449064,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:49:07.000Z","msg":"好過做雞"},{"pid":"e8f850ef6312e7201e1c7c6f9810b33ab7d825a4","tid":2449064,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n金融G得香港先有<br />\n日本妹好清純的"}]}